---
// templates/default/components/CTA.astro – Call-to-action section
---

<section class="py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%)">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">Ready to build your landing pages?</h2>
    <p class="text-indigo-100 text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Join hundreds of businesses already using LandingCraft to create beautiful, conversion-optimized landing pages.
    </p>
    <a href="/app"
       class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 rounded-xl bg-white font-bold text-lg shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition"
       style="color: var(--color-primary)">
      Start for free today
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
